## Example playbooks, using this role<a id="examples"></a>

Installation with automatic upgrade:

```yaml
---

- name: "Initialize the {{ namespace }}.{{ collection_name }}.run role"
  hosts: localhost
  gather_facts: false
  tasks:

    - name: "Trigger invocation of the {{ namespace }}.{{ collection_name }}.run role"
      ansible.builtin.include_role:
        name: "{{ namespace }}.{{ collection_name }}.run"
      vars:
        run_{{ collection_name }}_autoupgrade: true
```

Uninstall:

```yaml
---

- name: "Initialize the {{ namespace }}.{{ collection_name }}.run role"
  hosts: localhost
  gather_facts: false
  tasks:

    - name: "Trigger invocation of the {{ namespace }}.{{ collection_name }}.run role"
      ansible.builtin.include_role:
        name: "{{ namespace }}.{{ collection_name }}.run"
      vars:
        run_{{ collection_name }}_state: "absent"
```



